Name: Russian roulette
About the game: Famous gambling game with a revolver 'Russian Roulette'. This is the most extreme and dangerous gambling. The rules of the game are simple: only one bullet is inserted into the empty drum of the revolver, after which the drum turns. After that, the players in turn bring the muzzle of the revolver to their heads and pull the trigger. Check which side luck is on.
